    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2z71S07\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1140</a></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 750 gp</p>\r\n<p>This vibrant yellow and pale-green variety of seaweed has wide fronds with lines of narrow fringe along the upper edge.</p>\r\n<p><b>Gather</b> DC 25; <b>Yield</b> 1 dose</p>\r\n<p><b>Terrain</b> any underwater</p>\r\n<p><b>Preparation</b> A single dose of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/uncommon-races/arg-merfolk\">merfolk's</a> comb must be allowed to dry over a period of 7 days while being rubbed with alchemical oils once daily to prevent the herb from losing its properties during the process. This requires seven separate successful DC 14 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) checks, one every 24 hours during this week. If even one of those checks is a failure, the dose of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/uncommon-races/arg-merfolk\">merfolk's</a> comb is ruined.</p>\r\n<p><b>Use</b> Anyone who eats a dose of <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/races/other-races/uncommon-races/arg-merfolk\">merfolk's</a> comb gains the ability to breathe water as well as air for 8 hours.</p>\r\n",
